1. *Vratićemo* se kući večeras. (We will return home tonight.)
2. Nemojte da *vratićete* knjigu pre roka. (Don't return the book before the deadline.)
3. Ako ne *vratiš* dug do kraja meseca, platićeš kamatu. (If you don't repay the debt by the end of the month, you will have to pay interest.)
4. *Vratili* smo se s puta sinoć. (We returned from the trip last night.)
5. Nadamo se da će nam *vratiti* novac koji smo pozajmili. (We hope they will return the money we borrowed.)
6. Kada *budemo vratili* stvari, raspitaćemo se za novu školu. (When we return the items, we will inquire about a new school.)
7. Molim vas da mi *vratite* pasoš kada završite sa pregledom. (Please return my passport when you finish the inspection.)
8. *Vratiću* ti novac čim budem mogao. (I will return your money as soon as I can.)
9. Ne znam kako da mu *vratim* za sve što mi je učinio. (I don't know how to pay him back for everything he has done to me.)
10. *Vratimo* se na glavnu temu. (Let's get back to the main topic.)